Scenario: create form and add fields
Given basic organizational unit setup

When a value definition named SomeType is created
And a field definition named SomeField of type SomeType is created
And a form definition named SomeForm is created
And events are cleared
When a field definition is added to form
Then events fieldAdded occurred

When a field definition is removed from form
Then events fieldRemoved occurred

When a field definition is removed from form
Then no events occurred
